---
import "../../styles/global.css";
/* src/components/RecordKeeping.astro */
---

<div
  class="not-content my-8 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-md"
>
  <div class="border-b border-gray-100 bg-gray-50 px-6 pb-4 pt-6">
    <h3 class="mt-0 text-xl font-extrabold text-[#78081c]">Keeping Records</h3>
    <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600">
      Before lodging an application, start keeping clear and detailed records
      immediately
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="border-b border-gray-100 p-6 md:border-b-0 md:border-r">
      <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">
        Expenses to track
      </div>
      <ul class="m-0 list-none space-y-3 p-0">
        <li class="relative pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-700">
          <strong>Medical costs:</strong> General practitioner (GP), dental, and specialist
          fees
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-700">
          <strong>Counselling:</strong> Psychology or psychiatry costs
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-700">
          <strong>Travel:</strong> Fuel, parking, or public transport tickets for
          appointments
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-700">
          <strong>Lost income:</strong> Payslips or records of unpaid leave
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-700">
          <strong>Reports:</strong> The cost of obtaining medical evidence
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-gray-100 p-6 md:border-b-0">
      <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">
        Best practices
      </div>
      <ul class="m-0 list-none space-y-3 p-0">
        <li class="relative pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-700">
          <strong>Log it as you go:</strong> Use a simple notebook or phone note to
          record dates and costs immediately
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-700">
          <strong>Take photos:</strong> Receipts fade. Take a photo of every receipt
          and physical injury immediately
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-700">
          <strong>Digital backup:</strong> Email photos to yourself or save them in
          a secure private folder so they are not lost
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="border-t border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-6 py-4 text-sm text-rose-800"
  >
    <strong>Why is this important?</strong>
    These documents are essential to your claim and directly affect the amount of
    compensation awarded. You will need to attach copies to your application form.
  </div>
</div>
